  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK655">
<l>eṟṟeṉ ṟiraṅkuva ceyyaṟka ceyvāṉēṉ </l>
<l> maṟṟaṉṉa ceyyāmai naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let a minister never do acts of which he would have to grieve saying, "what is this I have done"; (but) should he do (them), it were good that he grieved not.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
